library(dplyr)
library(ggplot2)
library(HistData)
library(gridExtra)

glimpse(Minard.cities)
## Observations: 20
## Variables: 3
## $ long <dbl> 24.0, 25.3, 26.4, 26.8, 27.7, 27.6, 28.5, 28.7, 29.2, 30....
## $ lat  <dbl> 55.0, 54.7, 54.4, 54.3, 55.2, 53.9, 54.3, 55.5, 54.4, 55....
## $ city <fct> Kowno, Wilna, Smorgoni, Moiodexno, Gloubokoe, Minsk, Stud...
glimpse(Minard.temp)
## Observations: 9
## Variables: 4
## $ long <dbl> 37.6, 36.0, 33.2, 32.0, 29.2, 28.5, 27.2, 26.7, 25.3
## $ temp <int> 0, 0, -9, -21, -11, -20, -24, -30, -26
## $ days <int> 6, 6, 16, 5, 10, 4, 3, 5, 1
## $ date <fct> Oct18, Oct24, Nov09, Nov14, NA, Nov28, Dec01, Dec06, Dec07
options(scipen = 99999)
Minard.temp$date = c("18 out", "24 out", "9 nov", "14 nov", NA, "28 nov", "1 dez", "6 dez", "7 dez")

tema = theme(
  panel.background = element_rect(fill = "#FDFEF8"),
  panel.grid.major = element_line(colour = "white"), 
  panel.grid.minor = element_line(colour = "white"),
  plot.background = element_rect(fill = "#FDFEF8"),
  legend.background = element_blank(),
  legend.key = element_blank()
  )

top = Minard.troops %>%
  ggplot(aes(long, lat)) +
  geom_path(aes(size = survivors, colour = direction, group = group), lineend = "round", linejoin = "round") +
  scale_color_manual("Direção",
                     values = c("#D7C281", "gray"), 
                     labels = c("Avanço", "Recuo")) +
  scale_size("Sobreviventes", range = c(3, 12)) +
  ylab("Latitude") +
  xlab("") +
  geom_text(aes(label = city), data = Minard.cities) +
  coord_cartesian(xlim = c(24, 38)) +
  tema +
  theme(legend.position = c(.9, .2), legend.box = "horizontal") +
  ggtitle("Marcha de Napoleão em Moscou")

bottom = Minard.temp %>%
  na.omit() %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = long, y = temp)) +
  geom_line(col = "gray", size = 3) +
  geom_text(aes(label = date)) +
  ylab("Temperatura") +
  xlab("Longitude") +
  coord_cartesian(xlim = c(24, 38)) +
  tema 

grid.arrange(top, bottom, nrow = 2, heights = c(4, 2))
